

     
      He chuckles.  "You click once.  When you hear two clicks in reply, it means I'm there.  I may not show up right away but I'll be there quick as I can.  Go ahead try it."  You click yours once.  After a pause, you hear *click*click*.  He smiles at you and holds up a cricket of his own.  "See?"  He winks.  "I'll be listening."
     
    
